teresting places, you will find material like planks, nails, matches. With this material you can craft more advanced tools. Like bandages to heal your wounds, torches to give you light in the dark, or maybe some basic weapon. Your only goal that you have to follow is...to survive of course. Because while your body doesnt need water or food...he has to survive the horror of the woods. And what horrors they are.Because while the wood is already dark and creepy..its getting worse in the night. The horrors are to strong to survive them in the night, you have to hide inside your basement and do what you can to stay safe. Have you found some Planks to barricade the windows and doors? a beartrap perhaps to keep the mosters out? could you found fuel somewher to keeep your generator running so you can use the lights? And while you are hiding in a corner of the room, hoping that the horror will end to see the welcoming light of the new day...you know that what ever lurks in the woods will be back. And they will be hungry.A true masterpiece of an horrorgame, that could create all of his horror from its gameplay, and its intense immersion that is coming from the awesome visuals and the sounds. Ohh boy the sounds. I would recommend this game for everyone who likes horror games by any means. Its an experience that you will find no where else except this game."
