m to matter much. more of a slight inconvienence. I don't know if things change at the end due to number of deaths at the moment but it seems to change nothing other than you drop half your items that you can easily go find in a backpack where you died.overall 9/10 mostly cause of the control issues. To clarify I use a controller and every so often I die because it doesn't respond well due to the way it is designed. The keyboard mouse combo may work better but I would be surprized. Even with that issue this is easily one of the most entertaining games I have played and I am excited to explore some of the different paths that can be taken on new playthoughs.
