76561198086856738,Recommended,274520,35507522,Posted: 5 October,all,etegiwg,"If you haven't gutted a pig before, then this game is a must. Not only that, but you get to inject tainted meat into your bloodstream to give you super powers, but that's just a small part of the game. If you want an eerie experience throughout your play through, that's guaranteed.The top-down play style is a nice change from most games. It gives a new perspective, but just because you can see over walls doesn't mean you know where every bully is. You'll get bullied a lot. There's lots of bullies.I haven't finished the game yet, it's longer than expected, so that's a bonus. I dunno, maybe I'm just bad at it.Another nice touch is that you get buddies, just be sure not to kill them *cough* GaLm *cough.* Yeah there are characters that won't fight with you, but you can do a few quests and of course buy their junk.At night, you have to return to your hideout unless you like dying. I dunno, seems a bit inconvenient to me. Anyways, you can setup your hideout and try different methods of staying safe. Barricading windows and doors, running from people who wanna eat you, hiding. Ya know, the usual. If you die, you don't get paid the next morning, unless of course you're a WEIRDO that plays on hard mode...I say give it a shot. Watch some gameplay or play for a couple hours to see if it's for you. My only complaint is that there will probably never be a modding community, which is unfortunate, but it's still fun without a dubstep gun."
